# Thoughts

> A frictionless space for capturing observations, questions, half-formed ideas, and anything on your mind. No format required — just write.

---

## How to Use

1. **Just write** — Don't overthink format or structure
2. **Date entries** — Helps track when ideas emerged
3. **Be raw** — Unpolished thoughts are valuable
4. **Trust the process** — Claude will help process and act on these

---

## Processing Status

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| 🆕 | New — not yet reviewed by Claude |
| 🔄 | In Progress — Claude is working on it |
| ✅ | Processed — action taken or acknowledged |
| 💤 | Deferred — revisit later |

